neofontrender.tooltip.shadow_mode=Glyph mask skips color glyphs, fonts selected as Shadow font mask on the Font page, and code points in shadow.maskCodepoints; Emoji only skips Unicode emoji.
neofontrender.tooltip.fix_ime=Use GLFW's complete Unicode code point so emoji input is not truncated.
neofontrender.tooltip.fix_unicode_delete=Backspace and Delete remove one complete emoji instead of leaving half a surrogate pair.
neofontrender.tooltip.sign_paste=Allow Unicode clipboard text in the vanilla sign editor.
neofontrender.tooltip.hex_chat=Experimental: recognize #RRGGBB color markers, e.g. #FF0044red text. Skia/Cosmic only.
